Title: Project Dawn #2
Writer: Frank Spotnitz, Chris Ryan (based on the book by)
Actors: Philip Winchester, Sullivan Stapleton, Amanda Mealing, Eva Birthistle
Plot: Scott and Stonebridge discover that the terrorists in the hotel are searching for Mahmood. Grant learns that Latif's real goal is to capture a Pakistani chemical scientist who worked with the weapons inspection team in Iraq in 2003.
